      <title>台湾半导体 7 月份销售额飙升 45%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-09/taiwan-semiconductor-sales-soar-45-in-july-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾半导体制造公司 7 月份营收增长 45%，较 6 月份季度增长速度加快，并增强了人们对 Nvidia Corp. 等公司对人工智能芯片持续强劲需求的希望。彭博行业研究的 Mandeep Singh 正在主持“彭博未平仓合约”节目。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-09/taiwan-semiconductor-sales-soar-45-in-july-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 14:04:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>面向未来的亚洲可持续旅游业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-09/future-proofing-sustainable-tourism-in-asia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alta Capital Real Estate 首席执行官兼创始人 Rakesh Patel 和世界旅行及旅游理事会亚太区董事总经理 Liz Ortiguera 在新加坡举行的 2024 年彭博可持续商业峰会上与彭博的 K. Oanh Ha 讨论了亚洲可持续旅游和旅行行业的机遇和挑战。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-09/future-proofing-sustainable-tourism-in-asia</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 14:04:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Points Guy 称夏季旅行正在恢复正常</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-09/summer-travel-is-returning-to-normal-says-points-guy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《The Points Guy》主编 Clint Henderson 表示，夏季旅行正在恢复正常。他说，航空公司提供了很多优惠，酒店也开始降价。他正在接受《Bloomberg The Close》的采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-09/summer-travel-is-returning-to-normal-says-points-guy</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 13:50:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚公司因 24 亿美元外汇索赔纠纷陷入危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/nigerian-firms-in-crisis-over-2-4-billion-disputed-fx-claims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚一家制造业组织表示，由于尼日利亚央行未能结清 24 亿美元逾期外汇远期合约，尼日利亚企业正陷入“严重危机”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/nigerian-firms-in-crisis-over-2-4-billion-disputed-fx-claims</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 13:43:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴菲特抛售苹果股票将重塑主要股票指数</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/buffett-s-apple-share-dump-is-set-to-reshape-major-stock-gauges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃伦·巴菲特突然出售大量苹果公司股票，给这家 iPhone 制造商的投资者带来了意想不到的好消息：其在主要股指中的影响力将得到全面释放。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/buffett-s-apple-share-dump-is-set-to-reshape-major-stock-gauges</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 13:33:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国人民银行研究缩小利率走廊计划 警告债券风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/china-s-central-bank-studies-plan-to-narrow-its-rate-corridor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行表示，正在研究缩小短期利率波动区间的方案，扩大旨在更有效地引导市场的政策工具改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/china-s-central-bank-studies-plan-to-narrow-its-rate-corridor</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 11:16:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>紧张的国债市场迎来混乱的一周，收益率出现逆转</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/chaotic-week-for-nervous-treasury-market-features-u-turn-in-yields</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着对美国经济可能下滑的担忧 — — 曾引发美国国债价格上涨和短暂的市场崩盘 — — 逐渐消退 — — 全球债券市场动荡的一周逐渐平静下来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/chaotic-week-for-nervous-treasury-market-features-u-turn-in-yields</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市上涨；经济衰退担忧导致涨势减弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/european-stocks-rise-as-easing-recession-worries-boost-cyclicals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市周五小幅走高，但由于对美国经济可能陷入衰退的担忧挥之不去，四天的涨势有所减弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/european-stocks-rise-as-easing-recession-worries-boost-cyclicals</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 07:14:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西石油公司因税务协议意外亏损，但维持股息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/petrobras-maintains-dividend-after-tax-settlement-with-brazil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西国有石油生产商巴西石油公司（Petroleo Brasileiro SA）净亏损 26 亿雷亚尔（4.7 亿美元），令投资者感到意外，主要原因是首席执行官玛格达·尚布里亚德（Magda Chambriard）任职期间的首批业绩中出现了税务结算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/petrobras-maintains-dividend-after-tax-settlement-with-brazil</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 00:37:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经过几天的动荡，股市以低迷收尾：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在经历了疯狂的一周后，全球市场波动性出现历史性飙升，交易员仍保持谨慎，股市难以获得太大的上涨动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 22:20:57 GMT</pubDate>
